headline: Nasdaq Announces Mid-Month Open Short Interest Positions in Nasdaq Stocks as of Settlement Date January 15, 2026
summary: NEW YORK, Jan. 27, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- At the end of the settlement date of January 15, 2026, short interest in 3,515 Nasdaq Global MarketSM securities totaled 15,349,969,813 shares compared with 15,183,396,236 shares in 3,498 Global Market issues reported for the prior settlement date of December 31, 2025.
